thread.title: Laura Diana Chanel
thread.title_full: Crazy Factory bewertet von Laura Diana Chanel

author: Laura Diana Chanel
title: Laura Diana Chanel
text: I have orderd two septums in different orders. One I have only wore for 1 weekend and the second one I have worn more. While wearing it the jewels fell off, making it look ugly. When I wanted to put on the other one I also noticed that the jewels have fallen off.. I find it sad to see my beautifull septums die after only a month or so. I expected a better quality item.
